ding to the onset of a cold/hot\nsolution could be observed in timescales of the order of the dynamical time. A\nstrong turbulence implying supersonic velocities should permanently exist in\nthe multi-branch region of thick, stratified, pressure equilibrium media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Dec 2006 18:31:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
