. Our favoured explanation is that more massive black holes have larger\nvariability amplitudes, and we highlight the need for larger samples with more\ncomplete temporal sampling to test the robustness of this result.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Dec 2006 21:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
